<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-observa-listaDeUtilesEscolares" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>There are different categories.</li>
      <li>This looks like a list of school supplies.</li>
      <li>Some items are much more expensive than others.</li>
      <li>Some of the things have different options.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>What kinds of story books are available?</li>
      <li>Why are some things much more expensive than others?</li>
      <li>How much does the whole list cost if we buy everything on it for our class?</li>
      <li>What board games are available?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


